{"tid":2127351,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳洲媒體：武漢病毒所與巴基斯坦軍方合作研究新型傳染病。中國否認。","createTime":"2020-07-27T09:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T13:00:42.000Z","uid":48040,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"880a15d2bfc1ba9531538fe6c93bfb64874d6a0a","tid":2127351,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"澳大利亞一家出版物《克拉克森》（Klaxon）上週在其調查報告中指稱，北京和伊斯蘭堡已達成一項為期三年的秘密協議，&ldquo;以擴大潛在的生物戰能力，包括運行幾個與致命的炭疽劑有關的研究項目&rdquo;。中國武漢病毒學研究所&ldquo;出借了所有財政物資和科學支持&rdquo;。<span class=\"orange\">武漢實驗室</span>正在為巴基斯坦科學家提供&ldquo;病原體操作和生物信息學的廣泛的培訓&rdquo;，以幫助巴基斯坦開發自己的病毒收集數據庫。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐巴基斯坦大使館譴責澳大利亞媒體的報導是&ldquo;捏造&rdquo;的。中國大使館星期日在推特上說，&ldquo;這是完全不負責任的，惡毒的誹謗中國和中巴關係。作為一個負責任的國家，中國總是履行對《生物武器公約》的義務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1287675424546254849?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1287675424546254849%3Fs%3D20&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=e3247f40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1287675424546254849%3Fs%3D20&h=d73c646c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1287675424546254849?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"5769b474d6ae4dfcffb15434aae0aefeb621e83f","tid":2127351,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7ca36da7882bb281e1e5e864a3c0e9c1abd6e2","tid":2127351,"uid":199234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0214d1113453b2b69788304ffadf8e277702b1","tid":2127351,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill